task.summary: * Fixed bug that made extra pieces when 'two-touching' with drag and drop selected. * Changed board from marble, which looked too grainy, to earth/eggshell. * Fixed so that the chessboard always has the dark and light squares in the correct position (earlier the board did not rotate with the pieces).

MESSAGE.value: * Fixed bug that made extra pieces when 'two-touching' with drag and drop selected. * Changed board from marble, which looked too grainy, to earth/eggshell. * Fixed so that the chessboard always has the dark and light squares in the correct position (earlier the board did not rotate with the pieces).
